Random System Inter Trigger : Intermediare Banks

Links Banks :
   - Pcket TO Rs : link directly from MDI to parametrs 
    - IMPORTANT : Triggers to link to the Trigger of the Random System you want to animate  IMPORTANT 

Ui RS Report"
